@NODE history
@TITLE "cpumonitor · History"


    @{b}History@{ub}


    1.0 (25-Apr-04)   - first public release

    1.1 (26-Apr-04)   - fixed refresh bug in CPU Monitor class when window
                        was behind other window (thx. to itix for hint)

    1.2 (17-May-04)   - added vertical grid
                      - removed a small memory leak (DiskObject was not
                        freed)
                      - added DONOTACTIVATE tooltype, when activated
                        CPU Monitor opens with inactive window.
                      - added NOSIZEGADGET tooltype

    1.3 (10-Jun-04)   - second public release

                      - added BORDERLESS tooltype + additional required
                        functionality
                      - improved makefile

    1.4 (18-Jun-04)   - 3rd public release

                      - added DNETCFILTER tooltype

@ENDNODE

